00:14:09.930 --> 00:14:13.340
they don't all have to be the same format.

00:14:15.480 --> 00:14:20.660
As long as we can deterministically mux between them.

00:14:20.660 --> 00:14:22.840
As long as if you have one of these formats, there

00:14:22.840 --> 00:14:25.300
is a deterministic algorithm you can use to turn it into

00:14:25.300 --> 00:14:27.080
